    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical pre-owned market. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and a meticulously preserved interior cabin. Mechanical integrity is absolute, reflecting a history of uncompromising care and low-mileage stewardship. For the discerning driver seeking an unparalleled automotive investment, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
