    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It is honestly in incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I have taken such good care of it, and it really shows in every little detail. If you are looking for a ride that feels practically brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 46500.0,
