    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours-level condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis has been meticulously preserved, with documented subframe reinforcement and a fully overhauled VANOS system ensuring peak mechanical synchronization. The factory M-Variable differential lock provides exceptional torque vectoring, while the suspension remains tight and responsive, free of any bushing degradation. Finished in a flawless factory coat with an interior devoid of bolster wear, this is a turnkey example of BMW\u2019s finest naturally aspirated engineering.",
